data.description:
Renovated house with lots of outdoor space and storage. Perfect Southeast location! This rare find includes AIR CONDITIONING! Large lot, pets allowed, workshop, solar panels for reduced electric bills and more! Contact us for a tour. 

Location-
Central to East Portland and Gresham
Near Milwaukie, Oregon City, Gladstone and short commute to Downtown Portland

-Professional property management company
-Online payments and 24/7 maintenance line
-Large Lot
-Large Workshop
-Air conditioning 
-Washer Dryer
-Solar System allowing for reduced electric bills!

Contact us for a tour! Ready now!

Well behaved pets allowed for $50/mth/pet rent. 
Security Deposit is equal to one month's rent.
12 Month Lease.
NO Smoking on premises.
Tenant pays all utilities. Tenant responsible for landscaping.

Applications are $55/person. All occupants must fill out a separate application.

This ad is being posted on 12/18/23.. Applications accepted 12/18/23. Portland laws require landlords to process applications in the order received beginning 12/21/23. Applications received prior to 12/21 will be penalized with an 8 hr delay per law.

Landlord will use an individualized assessment to screen applicants. Reasons for screening denial may include:
1) Criminal conviction history
2) Derogatory credit history
3) Derogatory rental history
4) Income less than 2x the rental rate
5) Inability to verify application information
